text: Maria Evita "Ivy" Arago (born 6 August 1975, San Pablo, Laguna, Philippine) she is the Member of the Philippine House of Representatives from Laguna's 3rd district from 30 June 2007 to 30 June 2013. ==Personal life== Arago born in San Pablo, Laguna, Philippines in 6 August 1975. She is a Filipina politician. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Physicians Category:Politicians from Calabarzon Category:People from Laguna (province)
